{
  "name": "comitron",
  "displayName": "Comitron",
  "description": "%extension.description%",
  "version": "1.0.4",
  "publisher": "NianBroken",
  "author": "NianBroken",
  "icon": "media/icon.png",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/NianBroken/Comitron.git"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/NianBroken/Comitron",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/NianBroken/Comitron/issues"
  },
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.110.0"
  },
  "categories": [
    "SCM Providers"
  ],
  "activationEvents": [
    "onStartupFinished"
  ],
  "main": "./out/extension.js",
  "l10n": "./l10n",
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "comitron.generateCommitMessages",
        "title": "%command.generate.title%",
        "category": "Comitron",
        "icon": {
          "light": "media/light/ai-generate.svg",
          "dark": "media/dark/ai-generate.svg"
        }
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "scm/title": [
        {
          "command": "comitron.generateCommitMessages",
          "when": "scmProvider == git",
          "group": "navigation@50"
        }
      ]
    },
    "views": {
      "scm": [
        {
          "type": "webview",
          "id": "comitron.candidatesView",
          "name": "%view.candidates.name%",
          "icon": "media/view-icon.svg",
          "contextualTitle": "Comitron",
          "visibility": "visible"
        }
      ]
    },
    "configuration": {
      "title": "%config.title%",
      "properties": {
        "comitron.selectedTool": {
          "title": "%config.selectedTool.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "Codex",
            "ClaudeCode",
            "Gemini CLI",
            "API服务",
            "自定义"
          ],
          "default": "自定义",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 1,
          "description": "%config.selectedTool.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.selectedTool.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.detectedTools": {
          "title": "%config.detectedTools.title%",
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "default": [],
          "scope": "machine",
          "order": 2,
          "description": "%config.detectedTools.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.detectedTools.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.toolPath": {
          "title": "%config.toolPath.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "machine",
          "order": 3,
          "description": "%config.toolPath.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.toolPath.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.apiServiceJson": {
          "title": "%config.apiServiceJson.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "{\n  \"API地址\": \"https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions\",\n  \"API密钥\": \"sk-your-key\",\n  \"模型ID\": \"gpt-5-mini\",\n  \"自定义参数\": {\n    \"temperature\": 0.2,\n    \"top_p\": 0.9\n  }\n}",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 4,
          "description": "%config.apiServiceJson.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.apiServiceJson.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.promptTemplate": {
          "title": "%config.promptTemplate.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "基于下文提供的全部已更改文件内容与差异，生成 3 条可以直接提交的候选 Commit Message。\n\n语言要求：\n- 每条候选项的 title 与 description 均必须使用{{commitLanguage}}语言输出。\n\ndescription 字段要求：\n{{extendedDescriptionInstruction}}\n\n执行规则：\n1. 必须综合全部已更改文件进行归纳，不得仅描述其中的单个文件。\n2. 必须先判断本次提交的主要目的，再据此生成候选项。\n3. title 必须使用最合适的 Conventional Commits 前缀，可选值包括但不限于 fix:、feat:、build:、chore:、ci:、docs:、style:、refactor:、perf:、test: 等。\n4. 3 条候选项必须准确描述同一组改动，但在写法上需有所区分，文字不得重复。不同候选项之间的 Conventional Commits 前缀允许重复。\n5. title 必须为单行文本，表述明确、简洁，避免空话与模糊词汇，且结尾不得使用句号。\n6. 若改动点较多，title 只概括最核心的提交目的，不得堆砌细节。\n7. 只输出合法 JSON，不得输出任何解释、代码块标记、标题或其他额外文字。\n\n返回格式：\n{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"type: summary\",\n      \"description\": \"extended description\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"type: summary\",\n      \"description\": \"extended description\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"type: summary\",\n      \"description\": \"extended description\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n以下是当前仓库内所有已更改文件的内容与差异：\n{{changedFiles}}",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 5,
          "description": "%config.promptTemplate.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.promptTemplate.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.extendedDescriptionEnabledPrompt": {
          "title": "%config.extendedDescriptionEnabledPrompt.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "- 必须生成 Commit 描述，description 字段不得为空。\n- description 仅用于补充说明，不得重复 title 的内容。\n- description 必须采用列表格式，每一行为一条，以「- 」开头。\n- description 允许换行，但不得出现空行。\n- description 的表述应简洁、清晰，指向具体改动。",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 6,
          "description": "%config.extendedDescriptionEnabledPrompt.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.extendedDescriptionEnabledPrompt.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.extendedDescriptionDisabledPrompt": {
          "title": "%config.extendedDescriptionDisabledPrompt.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "- 不需要生成 Commit 描述。\n- 每条候选项的 description 字段必须返回空字符串。",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 7,
          "description": "%config.extendedDescriptionDisabledPrompt.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.extendedDescriptionDisabledPrompt.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.toolResponsePromptTemplate": {
          "title": "%config.toolResponsePromptTemplate.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "请根据标准输入中的内容生成结果，只输出合法 JSON，不要输出解释、标题、代码块或其他内容。",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 8,
          "description": "%config.toolResponsePromptTemplate.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.toolResponsePromptTemplate.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.responseJsonSchema": {
          "title": "%config.responseJsonSchema.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "{\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"required\": [\n    \"messages\"\n  ],\n  \"additionalProperties\": false,\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"messages\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"minItems\": 3,\n      \"maxItems\": 3,\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\n          \"title\",\n          \"description\"\n        ],\n        \"additionalProperties\": false,\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"title\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"minLength\": 1\n          },\n          \"description\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}",
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 9,
          "description": "%config.responseJsonSchema.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.responseJsonSchema.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.commitLanguage": {
          "title": "%config.commitLanguage.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "default": "简体中文",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 10,
          "description": "%config.commitLanguage.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.commitLanguage.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.contextBudget": {
          "title": "%config.contextBudget.title%",
          "type": "number",
          "default": 8192,
          "minimum": 512,
          "maximum": 65536,
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 11,
          "description": "%config.contextBudget.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.contextBudget.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.includeExtendedDescription": {
          "title": "%config.includeExtendedDescription.title%",
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 12,
          "description": "%config.includeExtendedDescription.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.includeExtendedDescription.markdownDescription%"
        },
        "comitron.uiLanguage": {
          "title": "%config.uiLanguage.title%",
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "zh-CN",
            "en"
          ],
          "enumItemLabels": [
            "简体中文",
            "English"
          ],
          "default": "zh-CN",
          "scope": "window",
          "order": 13,
          "description": "%config.uiLanguage.description%",
          "markdownDescription": "%config.uiLanguage.markdownDescription%"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "scripts": {
    "compile": "tsc -p ./",
    "watch": "tsc -watch -p ./",
    "vscode:prepublish": "npm run compile",
    "package:vsix": "vsce package",
    "publish:vsce": "vsce publish"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^25.5.0",
    "@types/vscode": "^1.110.0",
    "@vscode/vsce": "^3.9.0",
    "typescript": "^6.0.2"
  },
  "overrides": {
    "encoding-sniffer": "1.0.2",
    "glob": "12.0.0"
  }
}
